# Konflux ecosystem (downstream)

- **Platform:** [Konflux documentation](https://konflux-ci.dev/docs/) — Tekton pipelines, tenants, releases.
- **When changing** `upload`, global CLI, SBOM/artifact paths, or config paths in Tekton tasks that *run* pulp-tool: load **changing-pulp-upload** ([`skills/changing-pulp-upload/`](../../skills/changing-pulp-upload/)) and **[CLAUDE.md](../../CLAUDE.md)**.
- **When changing** `Dockerfile` or `.tekton/` container build PipelineRuns: load **changing-pulp-container** ([`skills/changing-pulp-container/`](../../skills/changing-pulp-container/)); Konflux builds the image — do not add GitHub Actions container jobs.
- **Workflow / code map:** [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) · [docs/ARCHITECTURE.md](../../docs/ARCHITECTURE.md)
